.RE
.TP
\f[CR]array.reverse()\f[R]
return a reversed copy of the array
.TP
\f[CR]array.map(fn)\f[R]
return a copy of the array where each element is the result of
\f[CR]fn(element)\f[R]
.TP
\f[CR]array.filter(fn)\f[R]
